descriptionHtml:
Place file in Skyrim game folder.

Type in console \"bat masks\" and you will get all Dragon Priests Masks (+ Wooden Mask)

After collecting the 8 Dragon Priest masks proceed to the barrow in Labrynthian (location of Wooden mask).Use Wooden Mask to travel back in time to the Dragon Priest Shrine. Place the 8 masks in each respective slot to !!unlock the reward Konahrik!!. You can also retrieve the other masks from the shrine before you return.
author: EvilPhoenix
